𝐍𝐚𝐭𝐚𝐩𝐨𝐬 𝐚𝐧𝐠 𝐦𝐚𝐡𝐚𝐛𝐚𝐧𝐠 𝐩𝐚𝐠𝐡𝐢𝐡𝐢𝐧𝐭𝐚𝐲... 𝐇𝐄𝐓𝐎 𝐍𝐀 𝐓𝐀𝐌𝐒!💌🔥

Matagal ka rin bang naghintay? 😮‍💨 𝐀𝐰𝐚𝐧𝐞𝐧, 𝐚𝐝𝐝𝐚𝐤𝐚 𝐦𝐞𝐭𝐭𝐞𝐧!

Buksan na ang inyong Outlook inbox 📩 dahil nagpadala na ng emails ang Far Eastern University - Red Cross Youth Council sa lahat ng aplikante, at masasabi mo na you have #VIGANToServeWithRCYC 🤠🐎

𝐀𝐠𝐛𝐢𝐚𝐠 𝐭𝐢 𝐑𝐂𝐘𝐂! 💚💛

#20getherInService
#Pu20NgBolunterismo
#TheGreenAndGoldStandardOfHumanitarianService
